Package: CellRomeR
Type: Package
Title: R package for phenotypic clustering of cell migration from microscopy data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Iivari Kleino, Laura L. Elo
Maintainer: MBC <mbc@utu.fi>
Description: Phenotypic clustering of cells based on their morphological and motility features from microscopy images. Utilizing advanced machine learning techniques and building on an iterative clustering projection method, CellRomeR offers a new approach to identify heterogeneity in cell populations.
Imports: XML,xml2,ggplot2,data.table,fastcluster,ILoReg,SingleCellExperiment,methods
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
